%H A105452 <a href="/index/Rec#order_06">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (0,0,2,0,0,-1).
%F A105452 a(3*n+1) = 7*n+2 = A017005(n), a(3*n+2) = 2*n+13, a(3*n+3) = 21*n+20.
%F A105452 From _Chai Wah Wu_, Sep 24 2020: (Start)
%F A105452 a(n) = 2*a(n-3) - a(n-6) for n > 6.
%F A105452 G.f.: x*(x^5 + 8*x^4 + 5*x^3 + 20*x^2 + 13*x + 2)/(x^6 - 2*x^3 + 1). (End)
%F A105452 E.g.f.: (9 + 7*exp(x)*(7*x - 1) + exp(-x/2)*(2*sqrt(3)*sin(sqrt(3)*x/2) - 2*(1 + 14*x)*cos(sqrt(3)*x/2)))/9. - _Stefano Spezia_, Jun 04 2026
